WEBVTT

00:03.504 --> 00:07.508
HEY, HOW´S IT GOING
WITH THE BOSS´ SON?

00:07.508 --> 00:10.010
I DON´T KNOW WHY MEL
HAD TO DUMP HIS KID ON ME.

00:10.010 --> 00:12.283
MOM, THAT GUY´S NOT CUT OUT
FOR ANYTHING AT THE FACTORY.

00:12.283 --> 00:14.485
HE´S GOT YOUR JOB DOWN.

00:16.717 --> 00:21.021
[ SCOFFS ]
AND TO THINK...

00:21.021 --> 00:25.196
MEL AND A DRUNK COCKTAIL
WAITRESS MADE THAT.

00:25.196 --> 00:27.158
I´M AWAKE.

00:27.158 --> 00:30.261
I DON´T CARE.
TELL YOUR DAD, WRITE ME UP.

00:30.261 --> 00:32.163
JUST REMEMBER MY NAME.

00:32.163 --> 00:34.305
I´M GINA FROM INSPECTING.

00:37.608 --> 00:40.341
LOOK, I DON´T KNOW
WHAT KIND OF PROBLEMS
YOU HAD AT YOUR SCHOOL,

00:40.341 --> 00:43.274
BUT WHEN YOU´RE HERE,
COME ON, MAN, YOU HAVE TO WORK.

00:43.274 --> 00:46.046
WHAT DID YOU HEAR
ABOUT ME IN SCHOOL?

00:46.046 --> 00:47.718
NOTHING.
IT´S NONE OF MY BUSINESS.

00:47.718 --> 00:50.781
DID YOU HEAR I GOT BUSTED
FOR STEALING A CAR?
YEAH.

00:50.781 --> 00:53.454
DID YOU HEAR
I PUNCHED OUT A TEACHER?
YEAH.

00:53.454 --> 00:55.586
DID YOU HEAR I KNOCKED UP
THE PRINCIPAL´S DAUGHTER?

00:55.586 --> 00:57.358
NO.

00:57.358 --> 01:00.831
OH. WELL, THAT JUST HAPPENED.
YOU´LL HEAR ABOUT IT NEXT WEEK.

01:02.733 --> 01:06.497
WELL, LOOK, ANYONE CAN FIGHT
AND STEAL AND KNOCK A GIRL UP.

01:06.497 --> 01:09.640
BUT IT TAKES A REAL MAN
TO FILE ALPHABETICALLY.

01:10.671 --> 01:12.773
GET CRACKING, THUG.

01:14.505 --> 01:17.478
WHO´S THE HOTTIE
IN THE PICTURE?

01:17.478 --> 01:19.180
THAT´S MY DAUGHTER.

01:19.180 --> 01:21.312
BUT SHE´S FAT AND UGLY NOW.
GO FILE.

01:24.385 --> 01:26.387
HEY, I´M ZACK...POWERS.

01:26.387 --> 01:28.519
WE WERE JUST
TALKING ABOUT YOU.

01:28.519 --> 01:31.592
YOUR DAD THINKS
YOU´RE FAT AND UGLY.

01:33.093 --> 01:34.465
OH, THAT´S FUNNY.

01:34.465 --> 01:37.668
HE MUST HAVE MISTAKEN ME
FOR HIS HEAD AND THAT TIE.

01:39.270 --> 01:41.602
I LIKE
THE SCHOOLGIRL LOOK.

01:41.602 --> 01:43.434
YOU GIRLS EVER WASH CARS
FOR CHARITY?

01:44.505 --> 01:48.209
GET ALL SOAPY?
FIGHT OVER THE HOSE?

01:48.209 --> 01:49.480
GEORGE...

01:49.480 --> 01:52.213
YOU...
STAY AWAY FROM MY DAUGHTER.

01:52.213 --> 01:54.114
AND YOU, CARMEN.
GO WAIT IN THE CAR.

01:54.114 --> 01:55.686
AND YOU...

01:56.787 --> 01:59.720
STOP BUYING ME
THESE UGLY-ASS TIES.

01:59.720 --> 02:01.892
MAX BOUGHT YOU THAT ONE.

02:01.892 --> 02:05.396
HA HA, I LOVE IT.
IT´S NICE.

02:05.396 --> 02:06.857
WE´RE ONLY HERE
FOR A MINUTE.

02:06.857 --> 02:10.331
SOMETHING...SPECIAL HAPPENED
TO MAX AT SCHOOL TODAY,

02:10.331 --> 02:12.833
AND HE WANTS TO TALK TO YOU
ABOUT IT.

02:12.833 --> 02:13.904
[ SIGHS ]

02:13.904 --> 02:17.408
OKAY, MAX.
LOOK...

02:17.408 --> 02:20.171
THERE´S NOTHING UNUSUAL
ABOUT THIS, OKAY?

02:20.171 --> 02:21.412
YOU´RE AT THAT AGE.

02:21.412 --> 02:22.773
NEXT TIME IT HAPPENS,

02:22.773 --> 02:24.675
JUST GET A STACK OF BOOKS
AND PUT THEM IN YOUR LAP

02:24.675 --> 02:26.847
AND REMEMBER THAT GOD
OR SANTA COULD BE WATCHING.

02:26.847 --> 02:32.183
I WON MOST-IMPROVED
SPECIAL-ED STUDENT OF THE MONTH!

02:32.183 --> 02:33.424
[ LAUGHS ]

02:33.424 --> 02:35.756
HEY, THAT´S GREAT, BUDDY.

02:35.756 --> 02:39.660
YEAH. THE SCHOOL EVEN GAVE ME
A BUMPER STICKER.

02:39.660 --> 02:42.733
YOU´RE SUPPOSED TO
PUT IT ON YOUR CAR.

02:42.733 --> 02:47.198
"PROUD PARENT OF THE
MOST-IMPROVED SPECIAL-ED...

02:47.198 --> 02:49.840
STUDENT."

02:49.840 --> 02:53.173
YOU KNOW WHAT?
I BET MOM´S CAR WOULD LOOK --

02:53.173 --> 02:55.676
ALREADY GOT ONE.

02:57.578 --> 03:00.411
SO WHAT DO YOU SAY
THAT WE CELEBRATE, HUH?

03:00.411 --> 03:02.283
ANYTHING YOU WANT.

03:02.283 --> 03:04.955
MOM´S TAKING ME TO DISNEYLAND
NEXT SATURDAY AND...

03:04.955 --> 03:07.658
I WANT TO KNOW
IF YOU CAN COME THIS TIME.

03:07.658 --> 03:09.820
SATURDAY...HUH?

03:09.820 --> 03:12.923
YOU´RE NOT SICK,
AND YOU DON´T HAVE TO WORK.

03:12.923 --> 03:14.795
[ LAUGHS ]
THANKS.

03:14.795 --> 03:17.528
YOU GOT ME THERE.
OKAY, DISNEYLAND IT IS!

03:17.528 --> 03:18.729
GREAT!

03:19.730 --> 03:21.732
OOH. DO YOU THINK
GRANDMA WANTS TO COME?

03:21.732 --> 03:24.335
[ SCOFFS ] NOT UNLESS
THEY REPLACED FRONTIERLAND

03:24.335 --> 03:26.537
WITH SMOKEY-DRINKY LAND.

03:34.345 --> 03:38.389
DISNEYLAND
WITH THE FAMILY.

03:40.991 --> 03:43.924
YOUR WIFE´S
PRETTY HOT, TOO.

03:43.924 --> 03:46.357
OKAY, FOR THE LAST TIME --

03:46.357 --> 03:50.000
THE WOMEN IN MY FAMILY
ARE OFF-LIMITS.

03:50.000 --> 03:53.464
EXCEPT THAT ONE.

03:53.464 --> 03:54.805
YOU WANT TO SEE THAT
ALL SOAPY

03:54.805 --> 03:56.607
WASHING YOUR CAR
IN A SCHOOLGIRL OUTFIT?

03:57.668 --> 03:59.940
I DIDN´T THINK SO.
WA-CHA!

04:01.742 --> 04:04.545
HEY.

04:04.545 --> 04:07.718
WHAT KIND OF CAR YOU GOT?

04:09.420 --> 04:11.822
[ INTRO TO WAR´S "LOW RIDER"
PLAYS ]

04:22.893 --> 04:27.438
♫ ALL MY FRIENDS
KNOW THE LOW RIDER ♫

04:57.328 --> 05:01.632
KIDS, WE GOT TO GO.
DISNEYLAND OPENS IN AN HOUR.

05:01.632 --> 05:04.304
YEAH, BIG DAY.
HURRY UP.

05:07.378 --> 05:09.039
I´M GOING TO DISNEYLAND!

05:10.681 --> 05:12.012
OH, MOM, WHY DO YOU ALWAYS
HAVE TO FILM EVERYTHING?

05:12.012 --> 05:14.715
BECAUSE THESE ARE
IMPORTANT MEMORIES.

05:14.715 --> 05:16.046
BUT WE NEVER WATCH
THE TAPES.

05:16.046 --> 05:17.888
STARTING THIS WEEK,

05:17.888 --> 05:20.821
EVERY SUNDAY
IS FAMILY-VIDEO NIGHT.

05:20.821 --> 05:23.994
AW!
WAY TO GO, CARMEN.

05:23.994 --> 05:25.956
WHY DON´T YOU JUST
REMIND MOM

05:25.956 --> 05:28.058
THAT WE HAVEN´T BEEN TO CHURCH
IN THREE SUNDAYS?

05:30.000 --> 05:33.564
IT HAS BEEN TOO LONG.
WE´RE GOING NEXT WEEK.

05:33.564 --> 05:34.905
AW!

05:34.905 --> 05:36.807
WHY DON´T YOU KIDS SHUT UP
BEFORE YOUR MOM

05:36.807 --> 05:38.709
SENDS ME ON A GOLF WEEKEND
WITHOUT MY FAMILY.

05:38.709 --> 05:40.671
DON´T YOU DO IT.

05:42.743 --> 05:44.475
GEORGE LOPEZ.

05:44.475 --> 05:45.976
ABOUT TO GO TO DISNEYLAND

05:45.976 --> 05:47.848
FOR THE FIRST TIME
IN HIS LIFE.

05:47.848 --> 05:49.049
SAY SOMETHING, HONEY.

05:49.049 --> 05:51.081
[ LAUGHS ]
WELL, I´M EXCITED, OKAY?

05:51.081 --> 05:53.353
IT´S FINALLY
GOING TO HAPPEN THIS TIME.

05:53.353 --> 05:55.055
NO EXCUSES.

05:55.055 --> 05:56.587
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

05:56.587 --> 05:58.559
WHAT ARE ERNIE AND RICKY
DOING HERE?

05:58.559 --> 06:01.061
OH, MAN.
AM I GLAD I CAUGHT YOU.

06:01.061 --> 06:02.833
LISTEN...

06:02.833 --> 06:04.935
SOCIAL SERVICES MOVED UP RICKY´S
FOSTER-CARE HEARING TO TODAY.

06:04.935 --> 06:07.898
IF YOU DON´T COME DOWN AS
MY CHARACTER WITNESS RIGHT NOW,

06:07.898 --> 06:09.640
I COULD LOSE HIM FOREVER.

06:09.640 --> 06:11.402
RIGHT NOW, RIGHT NOW?

06:11.402 --> 06:12.703
RIGHT NOW, RIGHT NOW.

06:14.605 --> 06:16.777
A HEARING ON A SATURDAY?

06:16.777 --> 06:19.480
UH, WELL, YOU KNOW
THE COURTS ARE ALL BACKED UP.

06:19.480 --> 06:21.452
GEORGE, PLEASE.

06:21.452 --> 06:22.853
YOU´VE GOT TO COME.

06:22.853 --> 06:24.985
OR THEY´RE GONNA TAKE RICKY
AWAY FROM ME.

06:24.985 --> 06:26.717
FOREVER.

06:31.722 --> 06:33.393
LOOK, BUDDY.

06:33.393 --> 06:35.395
YOU DON´T WANT YOUR FRIEND RICKY
TO END UP IN A BAD HOME,

06:35.395 --> 06:36.797
DO YOU, MAX?

06:36.797 --> 06:38.699
NO.

06:38.699 --> 06:41.872
WELL, LOOKS LIKE I´M NOT
GONNA BE ABLE TO GO TO
DISNEYLAND WITH YOU.

06:41.872 --> 06:43.834
Ricky: YOU GUYS ARE GOING
TO DISNEYLAND?

06:43.834 --> 06:45.436
I WANT TO GO!

06:45.436 --> 06:47.137
YOU´VE GOT
YOUR HEARING, RICKY.

06:47.137 --> 06:48.839
THERE´S NO HEARING.

06:48.839 --> 06:51.542
ERNIE WANTED ME TO LIE TO GET
MR. LOPEZ OUT OF SOMETHING.

06:54.615 --> 06:56.416
REALLY?

06:56.416 --> 06:58.519
ANGIE, PLEASE -- THIS KID BURNED
DOWN OUR GARAGE, STOLE OUR CAR,

06:58.519 --> 07:00.551
AND CRASHED IT
INTO THE FENCE.

07:01.922 --> 07:04.755
ARE YOU GONNA BELIEVE THE WORDS
OF A CLEARLY TROUBLED YOUTH

07:04.755 --> 07:06.927
OR THE WORDS OF
A LOVING AND SUPPORTIVE HUSBAND

07:06.927 --> 07:09.600
FOR THE LAST 17 YEARS
WE´VE [WHISTLES].

07:09.600 --> 07:12.062
GEORGE!

07:12.062 --> 07:14.805
RICKY, GET IN THE CAR.
YOU´RE GOING TO DISNEYLAND.

07:14.805 --> 07:16.006
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

07:16.006 --> 07:18.168
YOU TOO.
[ GIGGLES ]

07:18.168 --> 07:22.513
LOOK, MAX, I´M...

07:22.513 --> 07:24.615
LOOK,
I´LL MAKE IT UP TO YOU, MAN.

07:24.615 --> 07:26.717
WE CAN GO ANYWHERE...
ELSE YOU --

07:30.020 --> 07:32.052
COME ON, ANGIE,
YOU KNOW I HATE CROWDS.

07:32.052 --> 07:34.084
WAIT, WAIT, WAIT, WAIT.
I WANT TO GET THIS ON FILM.

07:34.084 --> 07:37.127
SO WHEN YOUR SON IS IN THERAPY
20 YEARS FROM NOW,

07:37.127 --> 07:40.661
HE KNOWS WHY YOU WOULDN´T
GO WITH HIM TO DISNEYLAND.

07:40.661 --> 07:42.232
SO, YOU WERE SAYING?
CROWDS?

07:42.232 --> 07:44.495
LOOK, ANGIE, YOU´RE MAKING THIS
WORSE THAN IT IS.

07:44.495 --> 07:46.136
OKAY, IF 20 YEARS FROM NOW,

07:46.136 --> 07:47.938
MAX HAS A GOOD-ENOUGH JOB
THAT HE CAN AFFORD A THERAPIST,

07:47.938 --> 07:49.770
I´LL TELL YOU
WHAT WE´RE GOING TO DO.

07:49.770 --> 07:51.872
WE´RE GONNA GO DOWN TO WHATEVER
BAR CARMEN IS WORKING AT,

07:51.872 --> 07:54.104
AND WE´RE GONNA --

08:15.165 --> 08:16.597
MOM.

08:16.597 --> 08:17.828
AH!

08:19.199 --> 08:21.271
WHY ARE YOU
STEALING MY FOOD?

08:21.271 --> 08:23.003
I´M NOT STEALING IT.

08:23.003 --> 08:25.105
THE WAY ANGIE COOKS,
I´M RESCUING IT.

08:25.105 --> 08:27.207
LOOK, YOU´RE NOT
GOING ANYWHERE.

08:29.009 --> 08:30.581
WHY DIDN´T YOU EVER
TAKE ME TO DISNEYLAND?

08:30.581 --> 08:31.782
WHAT?

08:31.782 --> 08:33.183
WE LIVED 40 MINUTES
FROM THERE.

08:33.183 --> 08:35.145
ALL MY FRIENDS WENT.
WHY DIDN´T YOU EVER TAKE ME?

08:35.145 --> 08:37.017
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT,
GEORGE?

08:37.017 --> 08:39.089
I TOOK YOU
WHEN YOU WERE 6 YEARS OLD.

08:39.089 --> 08:40.621
DON´T DO THIS.

08:40.621 --> 08:42.092
NO, LISTEN.

08:42.092 --> 08:44.555
IF YOU DON´T BELIEVE ME,
CHECK THE BACK OF YOUR ARM.

08:44.555 --> 08:47.027
THERE´S A SCAR THERE FROM WHEN
I DRAGGED YOU UNDER THE FENCE.

08:47.027 --> 08:50.130
YOU DID THAT
WITH YOUR FINGERNAIL

08:50.130 --> 08:54.264
TO MAKE THE SCHOOL THINK
THAT I HAD MY VACCINATIONS.

08:54.264 --> 08:58.538
ALL RIGHT, HERE´S THE TRUTH.
I SCREWED UP.

08:58.538 --> 09:00.110
I TOOK YOU ONCE,

09:00.110 --> 09:02.112
BUT YOU WERE TOO YOUNG
TO ENJOY IT.

09:02.112 --> 09:04.715
HOW COME
I DON´T REMEMBER?

09:04.715 --> 09:06.246
´CAUSE YOU WEREN´T
BORN YET.

09:07.778 --> 09:10.120
I THOUGHT MY WATER BROKE
ON THE MATTERHORN,

09:10.120 --> 09:13.253
BUT IT WAS JUST THE SPLASH
AT THE END OF THE RIDE.

09:13.253 --> 09:15.085
MOM!

09:15.085 --> 09:17.287
LOOK, I JUST HURT MY SON,

09:17.287 --> 09:19.690
BECAUSE I WOULDN´T GO
TO DISNEYLAND, AND DO
YOU WANT TO KNOW WHY?

09:19.690 --> 09:22.032
COULD YOU LEAVE IT
ON MY ANSWERING MACHINE?

09:22.032 --> 09:24.264
BECAUSE YOU RUINED IT
FOR ME.

09:24.264 --> 09:26.166
I DIDN´T WANT TO GO AND SEE
ALL THOSE KIDS HAVING FUN,

09:26.166 --> 09:27.838
BECAUSE IT WOULD JUST REMIND ME

09:27.838 --> 09:29.900
OF ALL THE OTHER THINGS
I DIDN´T HAVE GROWING UP --

09:29.900 --> 09:32.102
LIKE BIRTHDAYS OR CHRISTMAS,

09:32.102 --> 09:34.174
OR DOCTORS WITH OFFICES!

09:34.174 --> 09:37.648
WHAT KIND OF DENTIST
WORKS OUT OF A CAMPER?

09:39.249 --> 09:42.613
MOM, I HAD TO SPIT
OUT THE WINDOW!

09:42.613 --> 09:44.615
PARDON ME.

09:44.615 --> 09:46.657
LET ME
GET IN MY TIME MACHINE

09:46.657 --> 09:49.059
AND GO BACK
AND FIX YOUR CHILDHOOD.

09:49.059 --> 09:50.120
[ BEEPING ]

09:50.120 --> 09:51.591
OH, MY GOD, IT WORKED!

09:51.591 --> 09:54.594
LOOK, THERE´S A BIG BABY
IN FRONT OF ME.

09:54.594 --> 09:58.068
YOU JUST DON´T GET IT,
DO YOU?

09:58.068 --> 10:00.330
I´LL TELL YOU
WHAT I DON´T GET.

10:00.330 --> 10:04.334
IF TAKING YOUR KID TO DISNEYLAND
IS SUCH A BIG DEAL,

10:04.334 --> 10:07.177
THEN WHY AREN´T YOU THERE
WITH MAX?

10:07.177 --> 10:09.940
YEAH, YOU KNOW WHAT, MOM?
YOU´RE RIGHT.

10:09.940 --> 10:11.842
I SHOULD BE THERE.

10:11.842 --> 10:13.684
I´M GONNA STOP THIS NONSENSE
AND GO BE WITH MY FAMILY.

10:13.684 --> 10:15.285
I DON´T NEED ANY MORE
OF YOUR EXCUSES.

10:15.285 --> 10:17.287
I DON´T NEED
ANYTHING FROM YOU!

10:17.287 --> 10:19.619
I DON´T NEED YOUR BAD ATTITUDE!
I DON´T NEED ANYTHING!

10:22.723 --> 10:26.827
ERNIE BLOCKED ME IN!
I NEED A RIDE TO DISNEYLAND!

10:31.331 --> 10:33.834
MAN, THAT´S IT.

10:33.834 --> 10:37.107
THAT´S THE CASTLE TINKERBELL
FLIES OUT OF BEFORE THE MOVIES.

10:40.140 --> 10:42.142
YOU DON´T SAY.

10:42.142 --> 10:44.374
YOU THINK TINKERBELL
IS HERE?

10:44.374 --> 10:47.247
YEAH, I´M LOOKING
RIGHT AT HER.

10:48.849 --> 10:51.181
I CAN´T BELIEVE YOU GOT ME
TO COME IN HERE.

10:51.181 --> 10:53.724
LOOK, YOU´RE MY RIDE
IF I CAN´T FIND ANGIE.

10:53.724 --> 10:55.926
WHY DON´T I JUST WAIT FOR YOU
IN THE CAR, HUH?

10:55.926 --> 10:58.128
BECAUSE YOU´RE GONNA
GO TO THE NEAREST INDIAN CASINO

10:58.128 --> 11:00.230
AND LOAD UP
ON THE CHEAP SMOKES.

11:00.230 --> 11:02.362
THAT´S RIGHT,
I SAW YOU EYEING THE SIGN.

11:02.362 --> 11:04.234
HEY, WHY DON´T YOU
COME WITH ME?

11:04.234 --> 11:06.136
BE JUST LIKE
FRONTIERLAND,

11:06.136 --> 11:07.898
EXCEPT THIS TIME,
THE INDIANS WIN.

11:07.898 --> 11:10.170
I CAN´T BELIEVE I THOUGHT
I WOULD HATE THIS PLACE, MOM.

11:10.170 --> 11:11.702
IT´S AMAZING.

11:11.702 --> 11:13.273
WHAT´S AMAZING IS
THIS MANY PEOPLE

11:13.273 --> 11:15.145
THINK THEY LOOK GOOD
IN CARGO SHORTS.

11:15.145 --> 11:17.447
YOU KNOW, YOU JUST CAN´T
ADMIT THIS PLACE IS GREAT,

11:17.447 --> 11:19.209
BECAUSE THAT WOULD MEAN
ADMITTING

11:19.209 --> 11:21.882
TO BEING A HORRIBLE MOTHER
FOR NEVER BRINGING ME HERE.

11:23.453 --> 11:25.055
MOUSE EARS!

11:25.055 --> 11:28.058
I ALWAYS WANTED THOSE.
OLIVER!

11:28.058 --> 11:30.190
YOU SHOULD CHERISH THIS DAY!

11:30.190 --> 11:32.162
AND GET SOME SUN BLOCK.

11:33.363 --> 11:36.066
CAN WE PLEASE GO HOME NOW?

11:36.066 --> 11:38.398
COME ON,
THIS PLACE IS HUGE.

11:38.398 --> 11:40.300
WE´RE NEVER GONNA FIND
ANGIE AND THE KIDS.

11:40.300 --> 11:42.873
WE´RE GONNA SEARCH
EVERY INCH OF THIS PARK.

11:42.873 --> 11:46.376
FROM MR. TOAD´S WILD RIDE
TO SPLASH MOUNTAIN,

11:46.376 --> 11:48.809
AND THEN WE´LL GO OVER TO
DISNEY´S CALIFORNIA ADVENTURE

11:48.809 --> 11:51.211
TO SEE IF THEY´RE ON THAT NEW
TWILIGHT ZONE TOWER OF TERROR...

11:51.211 --> 11:54.114
AND BECAUSE I´M HERE
TO FIND MY FAMILY.

11:54.114 --> 11:58.048
OH, SORRY, KIDS.
HE´S NOT A CHARACTER.

11:58.048 --> 12:00.390
THAT´S HIS REAL HEAD.

12:05.455 --> 12:07.798
THAT WAS A LOT OF FUN,
WASN´T IT?

12:07.798 --> 12:09.399
THAT WAS GOOD.
I LIKED IT.

12:09.399 --> 12:11.331
OKAY,
WHAT SHOULD WE DO NEXT?

12:11.331 --> 12:13.904
OOH, RICKY AND I WANT TO
GO ON THE HAUNTED MANSION.

12:13.904 --> 12:16.807
UH...I DON´T KNOW.
ISN´T THAT A LITTLE SCARY?

12:16.807 --> 12:18.909
I MEAN, THE GHOSTS RIDE
IN THE CAR WITH YOU.

12:18.909 --> 12:21.772
AND YOU CAN SEE A WOMAN´S HEART
BEATING IN HER CHEST.

12:21.772 --> 12:23.313
THAT´S NOT SCARY.

12:23.313 --> 12:26.947
YEAH, WELL, JUST IN CASE,
YOU´D BETTER RIDE WITH ME,

12:26.947 --> 12:28.879
AND --
AND WE´LL HOLD HANDS.

12:28.879 --> 12:30.380
I CALL MIDDLE.

12:35.485 --> 12:37.487
HELLO?

12:37.487 --> 12:39.389
Did you have a good time
on Splash Mountain

12:39.389 --> 12:41.832
in your little,
green shirt?

12:41.832 --> 12:43.233
WHO IS THIS?

12:43.233 --> 12:46.937
Look behind you.

12:48.398 --> 12:50.340
WHAT ARE YOU
DOING HERE?

12:50.340 --> 12:52.072
I WANTED TO SEE YOU.

12:52.072 --> 12:54.805
YOU WERE FOLLOWING ME?
THAT´S CREEPY.

12:54.805 --> 12:56.276
NO, IT´S FLATTERY.

12:56.276 --> 12:58.478
IF MY DAD FOUND OUT YOU WERE
FOLLOWING ME, HE´D KILL YOU.

12:58.478 --> 13:00.210
YEAH, WELL,
YOUR DAD´S NOT HERE.

13:00.210 --> 13:01.852
DITCH YOUR FAMILY
AND COME WITH ME.

13:01.852 --> 13:03.483
ARE YOU CRAZY?

13:03.483 --> 13:05.255
ACCORDING TO
MY SCHOOL PSYCHOLOGIST,

13:05.255 --> 13:09.219
I´M ONLY A DANGER TO MYSELF
AND...[SIGHS] HOT GIRLS.

13:10.420 --> 13:12.392
HERE,
I GOT YOU SOMETHING.

13:12.392 --> 13:14.965
LOOK, MY DAD HAS TOLD ME
ALL ABOUT YOU.

13:14.965 --> 13:18.398
SO I DON´T WANT TO TALK TO YOU,
I DON´T WANT YOU FOLLOWING ME,

13:18.398 --> 13:20.831
AND I DON´T WANT ANYTHING
TO DO WITH YOU.

13:22.232 --> 13:24.935
OH, MY GOD, THAT´S A NECKLACE.
I WANT IT.

13:24.935 --> 13:28.378
I SAW YOU TRYING IT ON.

13:30.340 --> 13:32.512
Angie:
CARMEN?

13:32.512 --> 13:34.814
CARMEN!

13:34.814 --> 13:36.146
I BETTER GO.

13:36.146 --> 13:38.248
I´LL BE RIGHT BEHIND YOU.

13:39.219 --> 13:40.520
WAIT.

13:42.853 --> 13:46.256
YOU´D BETTER HIDE THIS.

13:50.030 --> 13:52.832
Max:
COME ON, MOM SAID WE HAVE TO
TAKE A PICTURE WITH GOOFY.

13:52.832 --> 13:54.464
DO IT WITHOUT ME.

13:54.464 --> 13:56.566
WE CAN´T.
YOU´RE GOOFY.

13:56.566 --> 13:58.468
[ LAUGHING ]

14:07.978 --> 14:09.880
[ CLATTERING ]

14:11.151 --> 14:12.883
HAVING FUN YET?!

14:12.883 --> 14:14.955
NO!

14:14.955 --> 14:17.157
HAVING FUN YET, MOM?!

14:17.157 --> 14:19.059
NO!!

14:19.059 --> 14:20.130
NOW?!

14:20.130 --> 14:21.291
NO!

14:23.133 --> 14:25.065
HOW ABOUT NOW?!

14:25.065 --> 14:26.997
NO-O-O-O-O-O-O!

14:33.403 --> 14:36.346
HI!
[ WHISTLES ]

14:36.646 --> 14:38.508
OH, THAT WAS AWESOME!

14:38.508 --> 14:40.310
YEAH, GREAT.

14:40.310 --> 14:42.482
YOU SIT IN A LOG
AND RIDE OVER A WATERFALL.

14:42.482 --> 14:45.215
THAT´S HOW THE CANADIANS
SNEAK INTO THE COUNTRY.

14:45.215 --> 14:47.317
MOM, COME ON.
I KNOW YOU HAD FUN.

14:47.317 --> 14:49.189
NO, I DIDN´T.

14:49.189 --> 14:50.460
REALLY?

14:50.460 --> 14:52.662
THEN WHY ARE YOU SMILING
IN THIS PICTURE?

14:55.365 --> 14:58.068
ALL RIGHT, I HAD FUN.

14:58.068 --> 15:00.130
IMAGINE THAT LOOK ON MY FACE
AS A KID!

15:00.130 --> 15:02.102
GEORGE, LOOK AROUND YOU.

15:02.102 --> 15:03.573
WHY WOULD I SHOW YOU
A PLACE

15:03.573 --> 15:07.077
WITH ALL THESE HAPPY FAMILIES
HAVING A GREAT TIME,

15:07.077 --> 15:10.080
AND THEN TAKE YOU BACK
TO THE DUMP WE LIVED IN?

15:10.080 --> 15:12.112
YOU WOULD HAVE BEEN MISERABLE.

15:12.112 --> 15:15.915
SO TO KEEP ME FROM BEING SAD,
YOU MADE SURE I WAS NEVER HAPPY?

15:15.915 --> 15:20.520
GEORGE, IF CRAP IS ALL YOU KNOW,
THEN IT´S NOT CRAP.

15:20.520 --> 15:22.452
IT´S NORMAL.

15:22.452 --> 15:24.524
MOM, WHEN YOU´RE A LITTLE BOY

15:24.524 --> 15:26.456
AND YOUR BED IS SURROUNDED
WITH RAT TRAPS,

15:26.456 --> 15:28.999
AND YOU´RE JEALOUS BECAUSE
THE RATS ARE GETTING CHEESE,

15:28.999 --> 15:30.660
YOU KNOW IT´S CRAP!

15:32.462 --> 15:34.534
GOD, YOU´RE SO MESSED UP,
YOU DON´T EVEN KNOW

15:34.534 --> 15:37.007
HOW TO HAVE A GOOD TIME
WITH YOUR OWN FAMILY.

15:37.007 --> 15:38.438
HEY...

15:38.438 --> 15:40.971
THERE´S YOUR FAMILY OVER THERE.
GO BE NORMAL.

15:40.971 --> 15:43.013
I WILL. I´LL GO ON
ALL THE RIDES WITH THEM.

15:43.013 --> 15:46.316
I´LL EAT WITH THEM, I´LL WAIT
WHILE THEY GO TO THE BATHROOM,

15:46.316 --> 15:47.647
I´LL WAIT WHILE ANGIE

15:47.647 --> 15:50.250
VIDEOTAPES EVERYTHING
THAT SHE SEES.

15:51.281 --> 15:54.084
TWO CAN MOVE FASTER
THAN SEVEN.

15:54.084 --> 15:56.486
VAMONOS!

16:04.494 --> 16:07.437
HEY, I KNOW IT´S THE NEW
TWILIGHT ZONE TOWER OF TERROR,

16:07.437 --> 16:09.139
BUT DON´T BE SCARED.

16:09.139 --> 16:11.041
I HEAR IT´S A 13-STORY DROP.

16:12.542 --> 16:15.245
PROTECT ME,
GRANDMA CARDENAS.

16:18.248 --> 16:20.710
MY MOM´S GONNA SEE YOU.

16:20.710 --> 16:24.314
I GOT SOMETHING ELSE
I WANT TO GIVE TO YOU.

16:31.061 --> 16:32.322
[ SCREAMING ]

16:38.068 --> 16:40.170
HAVING A GOOD TIME,
HONEY?

16:40.170 --> 16:42.132
WHY? WHAT DID YOU SEE?

16:42.132 --> 16:44.204
YOU´VE BEEN SMILING.

16:44.204 --> 16:45.375
[ GIGGLES ]

16:45.375 --> 16:47.477
WELL,
THIS DAY HAS BEEN...

16:47.477 --> 16:50.240
A LOT MORE FUN
THAN I THOUGHT IT WOULD BE.

16:50.240 --> 16:52.212
GOOD.

16:52.212 --> 16:54.244
I WANT TO DO
THE TEACUPS.

16:54.244 --> 16:56.146
TEACUPS
ARE FOR BABIES.

16:56.146 --> 16:57.487
NO,
THEY´RE FOR EVERYONE.

16:57.487 --> 16:59.319
LOOK, THERE´S SOME GROWN-UPS
ON THEM.

17:05.625 --> 17:07.026
GEORGE?

17:08.428 --> 17:10.700
OH, MY GOD, I THOUGHT YOU WERE
GONNA GET SICK, MOM.

17:10.700 --> 17:12.031
HEY.
HEY.

17:12.031 --> 17:14.234
[ Laughing ]
HEY.

17:14.234 --> 17:16.366
DAD, WHAT ARE YOU
AND GRANDMA DOING HERE?

17:16.366 --> 17:18.238
I FELT BAD
ABOUT NOT BEING WITH YOU,

17:18.238 --> 17:19.739
SO I CAME DOWN
TO FIND YOU.

17:19.739 --> 17:21.771
MAN, WHERE YOU BEEN?
I´VE BEEN LOOKING EVERYWHERE!

17:21.771 --> 17:23.443
ON THE TEACUPS?

17:23.443 --> 17:25.645
YEAH, THAT WAY
I COULD LOOK EVERYWHERE AT ONCE.

17:25.645 --> 17:28.318
WA-CHA...

17:28.318 --> 17:30.550
YOU MISSED
ALMOST THE WHOLE DAY.

17:30.550 --> 17:33.052
I´M SORRY I COULDN´T BE HERE,
BUT LET ME MAKE IT UP TO YOU.

17:33.052 --> 17:34.584
NEXT WEEKEND,

17:34.584 --> 17:36.626
WE´LL COME DOWN HERE EARLY,
WE´LL GO ON ALL THE RIDES,

17:36.626 --> 17:38.057
IT´LL BE A GUY´S DAY.

17:38.057 --> 17:39.589
ME AND YOU, MAX.

17:39.589 --> 17:43.093
NO, ´CAUSE NEXT WEEKEND,
I HAVE TO STUDY FOR A BIG TEST.

17:43.093 --> 17:45.195
WELL, I DON´T.
I´LL BE HERE.

17:57.547 --> 18:00.550
CAN I WAKE DAD UP
TO SAY "GOOD NIGHT"?

18:00.550 --> 18:02.852
NO, HONEY.
LET HIM SLEEP.

18:02.852 --> 18:04.314
YEAH, YOU´RE RIGHT.

18:04.314 --> 18:06.386
THE LITTLE FELLA´S
HAD A BIG DAY.

18:11.861 --> 18:15.094
♫ YO HO, YO HO ♫

18:15.094 --> 18:17.797
♫ A PIRATE´S LIFE FOR ME ♫

18:17.797 --> 18:20.230
THE DOG HAS THE KEYS!

18:29.479 --> 18:30.840
MOM...

18:30.840 --> 18:34.113
WHAT ARE YOU
DOING HERE?

18:34.113 --> 18:37.147
NOTHING.
I FORGOT MY SMOKES.

18:37.147 --> 18:39.149
WHAT´S THIS?

18:39.149 --> 18:41.821
I DON´T KNOW.
IT´S YOUR YARD.

18:46.826 --> 18:49.229
MY EARS.

19:01.271 --> 19:03.743
THANKS, MOM.

19:03.743 --> 19:05.575
YEAH, YEAH, YEAH.

19:05.575 --> 19:07.417
YOU KNOW, IT´S A GOOD THING

19:07.417 --> 19:10.580
YOU DIDN´T HAVE THOSE EARS
WHEN YOU WERE A KID.

19:10.580 --> 19:13.223
YOU WOULD HAVE GOTTEN
YOUR BUTT KICKED.

19:13.223 --> 19:16.356
KIDS DON´T BEAT YOU UP
FOR WEARING MOUSE EARS.

19:16.356 --> 19:18.228
I WOULD HAVE DONE IT.

19:33.172 --> 19:38.508
WELL, YOU´RE HOME LATE.
AREN´T YOU, DAD?

19:38.508 --> 19:41.651
SORRY, MAX,
I HAD TO WORK.

19:41.651 --> 19:44.514
THERE´S A LOT OF PARTS
COMING IN...AND DELAYS.

19:44.514 --> 19:45.655
REALLY?

19:45.655 --> 19:47.787
´CAUSE I CALLED THE FACTORY,

19:47.787 --> 19:51.261
AND THEY SAID YOU LEFT EARLY
WITH A TUMMYACHE.

19:51.261 --> 19:53.363
I WENT TO THE DOCTOR, MAX.
YOU DIDN´T SEE ME AT LUNCH.

19:53.363 --> 19:55.265
I WAS LIKE, "UGH."

20:08.578 --> 20:09.979
I KNEW IT!

20:09.979 --> 20:12.642
YOU WENT TO DISNEYLAND
WITHOUT ME.

20:12.642 --> 20:15.285
MAX, IT´S NOT
WHAT IT LOOKS LIKE.
